text.tspan: Astronauts exploring the Metaverse in their bubble
boats, Alberts come from a highly evolved
civilization created by the crypto community. Alberts
are equipped with gadgets and gears that allow
them to traverse any terrain and overcome any
Once you purchase a bubble boats, you will find a
unique combination of an Albert and a toolbox of
five parts that generates either a Rover Albert, an
Avian Albert, or an Orca Albert. The toolbox includes
a space suit, a face shield, a flower badge, an arm
bag, and protective wear for the ears, hands, and
feet. All five parts in the toolbox can then be
unbundled and traded separately, in order to change
the Albert’s appearance and expand its abilities.
After trading the parts to create the ultimate Albert
for you, it can be minted into its final form.
To encounter an Albert, invite their spacecraft The Bubble Boat to land
